summary: This is an email from May 3, 2021, with the subject 'Call re Maxwell photo metadata', indicating a communication about a call concerning photo metadata related to Ghislaine Maxwell. It appears to be an external email forwarded or sent to FBI personnel in New York.

events.title: Email regarding Maxwell photo metadata call

keyFacts: The document is an email dated May 3, 2021, concerning a call about photo metadata related to Ghislaine Maxwell.
The email is marked as external and was sent to or from FBI personnel in New York (USANYS).
The subject suggests ongoing investigative activity regarding digital evidence (photo metadata) in the Maxwell case in 2021.
